{
  "stem": "13623.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that meant life or death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He lives in-- I haven't seen him in many years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lives somewheres in New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huna Malik.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No relationship.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just met there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were teamed up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got to be partners in this carrying of this box all day long.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of us-- none of us had any-- any kind of personal problems with each other, except there were people that would steal bread from other people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- people would want to push in line while we were standing to receive our soup, people would push in front of each other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But other than that, there was-- there was not a problem between the prisoners, we-- among the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After I was working there for a while, and it was-- it wasn't a pleasant job, I was assigned to the SS kitchen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was doing the dirty work, like washing pots and pans, peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was a lifesaver to me, because they had all the food that they-- food that we forgot exists, like sugar, eggs, bread, the best-- the best that they could get.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and the prisoners had a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were two different kitchens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And their kitchens, suffice-- suffice to say, is-- was a lot different than the prisoners' kitchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I learned the ropes to steal food and bring it in to my fellow friends and people that I knew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bread, sugar, butter, whatever I can put my hands on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And other people like me that worked in that kitchen did that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had my sort of my group of kids that-- and people that I helped with food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know everybody in that-- in that detail.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
